{"title":"2021 Propain Yuma kids full suspension mountain bike grows with them","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/06/22/2021-propain-yuma-kids-full-suspension-mountain-bike-grows-with-them/","date":1624352446000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>The moment has come. There’s no denying it anymore. You’ve accepted that your kid is faster than you! Is it time to give them the upgrade their skills deserve? Propain Bikes have a long history of developing high end full suspension mountain bikes for the young rider. Today, they launch the 2021 Propain Yuma, with a reduced standover height to fit more riders. Here’s everything you need to know.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22041837/propain-yuma-bad-mint-kids-full-suspension-mtb-140mm-travel.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22041837/propain-yuma-bad-mint-kids-full-suspension-mtb-140mm-travel.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x323/rscb18/ng:webp/ngcb18\" alt=\"propain yuma kids fully mtb\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22041837/propain-yuma-bad-mint-kids-full-suspension-mtb-140mm-travel.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22041837/propain-yuma-bad-mint-kids-full-suspension-mtb-140mm-travel-297x198.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22041837/propain-yuma-bad-mint-kids-full-suspension-mtb-140mm-travel-800x533.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22041837/propain-yuma-bad-mint-kids-full-suspension-mtb-140mm-travel-120x80.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s