ontent/uploads/2021/06/22031823/propain-yuma-kids-mtb-shock-frame-bag-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031823/propain-yuma-kids-mtb-shock-frame-bag-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031823/propain-yuma-kids-mtb-shock-frame-bag-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-262446\">The Yuma comes with a frame bag for snacks and spares, and the front triangle fits a 500ml water bottle too</figcaption></figure><p>The new Propain Yuma gets a few important changes for 2021. It maintains a 140mm travel fork, but drops the rear wheel travel by 5mm to match it. The frame height is where we see the biggest change, reducing by a significant 32mm down to 320mm. The resulting lower standover height will mean more riders have a better fit, and will be able to straddle the bike more comfortably when stopped at the trail side.</p><figure id=\"attachment_262443\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-262443\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031804/propain-yuma-kids-full-suspension-mtb.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031804/propain-yuma-kids-full-suspension-mtb.jpg\" alt=\"propain yuma kids full suss mtb\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031804/propain-yuma-kids-full-suspension-mtb.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031804/propain-yuma-kids-full-suspension-mtb-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031804/propain-yuma-kids-full-suspension-mtb-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031804/propain-yuma-kids-full-suspension-mtb-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031804/propain-yuma-kids-full-suspension-mtb-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031804/propain-yuma-kids-full-suspension-mtb-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031804/propain-yuma-kids-full-suspension-mtb-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031804/propain-yuma-kids-full-suspension-mtb-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb18 src ng ngcb18 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031804/propain-yuma-kids-full-suspension-mtb.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031804/propain-yuma-kids-full-suspension-mtb.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031804/propain-yuma-kids-full-suspension-mtb-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031804/propain-yuma-kids-full-suspension-mtb-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031804/propain-yuma-kids-full-suspension-mtb-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031804/propain-yuma-kids-full-suspension-mtb-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031804/propain-yuma-kids-full-suspension-mtb-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031804/propain-yuma-kids-full-suspension-mtb-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031804/propain-yuma-kids-full-suspension-mtb-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-262443\">The Acros frame bearings are protected by Propain Dirt-Shields; extra seals protect the bearings from dust, water and dirt.</figcaption></figure><p>Propain have also reduced the weight of the aluminium frame by 100g, now weighing a claimed 2.7kg. Plus, with the updated and lighter parts list, the complete bike now weighs in at 12.7 kg.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031742/propain-yuma-2021-kids-full-suspension-mtb.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031742/propain-yuma-2021-kids-full-suspension-mtb.jpg\" alt=\"propain yuma 2021\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031742/propain-yuma-2021-kids-full-suspension-mtb.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031742/propain-yuma-2021-kids-full-suspension-mtb-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031742/propain-yuma-2021-kids-full-suspension-mtb-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031742/propain-yuma-2021-kids-full-suspension-mtb-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031742/propain-yuma-2021-kids-full-suspension-mtb-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031742/propain-yuma-2021-kids-full-suspension-mtb-696x464.jpg 