. It should be noted that this is unaffected by swapping from 24″ to 26″ wheels. So, while some dimensions of the bike will be improved for a taller rider, not everything grows proportionally.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031810/propain-yuma-kids-mtb-cockpit.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031810/propain-yuma-kids-mtb-cockpit.jpg\" alt=\"propain yuma 2021 kids mtb cockpit 680mm handlebar\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031810/propain-yuma-kids-mtb-cockpit.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031810/propain-yuma-kids-mtb-cockpit-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031810/propain-yuma-kids-mtb-cockpit-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031810/propain-yuma-kids-mtb-cockpit-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031810/propain-yuma-kids-mtb-cockpit-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031810/propain-yuma-kids-mtb-cockpit-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031810/propain-yuma-kids-mtb-cockpit-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031810/propain-yuma-kids-mtb-cockpit-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb18 src ng ngcb18 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031810/propain-yuma-kids-mtb-cockpit.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031810/propain-yuma-kids-mtb-cockpit.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031810/propain-yuma-kids-mtb-cockpit-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031810/propain-yuma-kids-mtb-cockpit-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031810/propain-yuma-kids-mtb-cockpit-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031810/propain-yuma-kids-mtb-cockpit-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031810/propain-yuma-kids-mtb-cockpit-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031810/propain-yuma-kids-mtb-cockpit-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031810/propain-yuma-kids-mtb-cockpit-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>The 24″ complete bike comes with a 40mm stem, so there is some scope to increase reach with a longer stem, up and to a point. Propain recommend the 24″ configuration for riders 125cm to 150cm, reserving the 26″ wheels for a height range of 140cm to 155cm.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031748/propain-yuma-aluminium-kids-mtb-internal-cable-routing.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22031748/propain-yuma-aluminium-kids-mtb-internal-cable-routing.jpg\" alt=\"propain yuma internal cable routing alloy frame\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.c